<div id="c1">
<p>Have you ever seen the &#8220;Leap Pad&#8221; products? They do pretty much exactly what you describe here, and are a lot more Fisher-Price-durable than any iPad. My youngest is in 4th grade now, but there&#8217;s no way I would have let her near an iPad-scale device while she was at learning-to-read age. It&#8217;s a good thing that Leap Pad was TOUGH!</p>

<p>Walter</p>

