<div id="c10">
<p>How have (or could) these ideas be applied to adults learning a second language? Since reading seems to be a less &#8220;primal&#8221; language ability, should initial adult language learning be entirely aural (as it certainly is in some immersion programs)?</p>

<p class="posted">posted by <a rel="nofollow" href="http://pwhite.org">Patrick White</a>
 on March 30, 2010 <a href="readingmachine#c10" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
